name: Om Dusupay Gateway Woocommerce
author: Siddharth Singh

sections.description:
This plugin just add Dusupay Payment Gateways for WooCommerce. So you can change name Merchant id of Payment Gateways as per your requrements.

sections.installation:
1. Upload the plugin to the ‘/wp-content/plugins/’ directory
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
  3. Go to WooCommerce > Setting > Payment Gateways Then Active & configure WooCommerce Custom Payment Gateways
sections.faq: Please contact with us directly if you have any problem to install or use the plugin.
